text: Prince Mabandla Ndawombili Fred Dlamini (born 11 November 1930)Profile of Mabandla Dlamini is a Eswatini politician. He was Prime Minister of Swaziland from 23 November 1979 to 25 March 1983. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of Eswatini
title: Mabandla Dlamini
